			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Non-critpath. A human adventurer accuses a tiefling child of stealing a necklace from him. A tiefling guard may intervene if things get out of hand. &#xA;&#xA;Barth: Angry, but gruff and restrained. &#xA;Meli: Fearless, urging Barth on. " />
